# McLib API Structure

## McLibProvider.api – Entry Point

McLib is accessed exclusively via `McLibProvider.api`:

```kotlin
import net.developertobi.mclib.api.McLibProvider

// Access all McLib functionality
McLibProvider.api.formatRegistry
McLibProvider.api.formatController
McLibProvider.api.localizationController
McLibProvider.api.persistentDataController
McLibProvider.api.sidebarController
McLibProvider.api.teamController
McLibProvider.api.commandController
McLibProvider.api.yamlConfigController
McLibProvider.api.jsonConfigController
```

## McLib Module Structure (Reference)

- **mclib-api**: Interfaces, abstract types, contracts – no implementation
- **mclib-plugin**: Implementations under `net.developertobi.mclib.bukkit.api.*`

The API is set in `McLibProvider.api` by the plugin on startup.

## Dependency

Plugins that use McLib:

```kotlin
dependencies {
    compileOnly("net.developertobi.mclib:mclib-api:1.0-SNAPSHOT")
}
```

Repository: `https://maven.pkg.github.com/tobiasheimboeck/McLib`
